  "detailed_description": "<strong>Game Store Simulator is about buy and sell video games, its perfect fit for game enthusiasts and managment simulation lovers. Buy cheap and sell for profit, expand your business.<br><br>Get in your vehicle, fill up the gas and be careful because your vehicle may be damaged on the roads! Deliver the cargo safely. Go to market and buy some games, and load it to your vehicle. Stop front of the advertisement company if you want to increase your popularity. Sell your games, decorate your store and satisfy your customers</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/0a5f98d4f16e2b1fbe4f65d420bc26f2.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/05bc3e4db6ef382915535ea294cbe908.poster.avif?t=1726887346\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/05bc3e4db6ef382915535ea294cbe908.webm?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/05bc3e4db6ef382915535ea294cbe908.mp4?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sell Games :</h2><strong>limitless variety for placing video games to your shelfs. You can make any flag shape you want.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/c0a679402c97678306dc008489cc1fdd.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/710afbeeaac71cee352ef664d6f51cd1.poster.avif?t=1726887346\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/710afbeeaac71cee352ef664d6f51cd1.webm?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/710afbeeaac71cee352ef664d6f51cd1.mp4?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maintenance :</h2><strong>Don't forget to take care of your vehicle! No one wants to be stranded. You can fill up with gas and fix your vehicle if it's damaged</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/8b54171bda9d23175d3f83b9ebfdc3af.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/c0405f0d33cd13f8b2317f2b8fc415c7.poster.avif?t=1726887346\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/c0405f0d33cd13f8b2317f2b8fc415c7.webm?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/c0405f0d33cd13f8b2317f2b8fc415c7.mp4?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hire Worker :</h2><strong>Hire a worker to make things much easier for you, and your sales will take care of themselves.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/ac211cae121268bc05dbde804c91f8fa.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/7c67c4606b362173a63b060a9a9f89c4.poster.avif?t=1726887346\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/7c67c4606b362173a63b060a9a9f89c4.webm?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/7c67c4606b362173a63b060a9a9f89c4.mp4?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand :</h2><strong>You don’t need to stay small. You can expand your game store to be able to serve more customers.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/0f0bfd95558b99e01845d1116c053f68.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/42f34bf1e66f7c94e659e8724b6d407b.poster.avif?t=1726887346\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/42f34bf1e66f7c94e659e8724b6d407b.webm?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/42f34bf1e66f7c94e659e8724b6d407b.mp4?t=1726887346\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate :</h2><strong>Decorate your store however you like in a wide array of options and satisfy your customer even more.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2598930/extras/a9a51bb91b2d9a97c7e6bbf5be501a12.avif?t=1726887346\" width=600 height=126 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a